body:
![Zaheer](https://zaheercena.files.wordpress.com/2016/08/10984620_866635366745231_909352633323423715_n.jpg?w=960)
### This is Introduction
### EARLY LIFE.
This is Zaheer Ahmed born in Soon Valley Sakesar (District Khushab) in 14, Aug 1993. Zaheer completed his primary education from a Minhaj-ul-Quran School and after in July 2000 he moved to Jauharabad city known as Atomic City in World and continued his Education. In Jauharabad he begin his Journey to achievements for education. He get first in Primary Board of Sargodha Division. Later in 2005 he faced medical issues and scored 40% in middle and following this in 2007 he again successfully achieved good percentage.

### COLLAGE LIFE
In beginning on Collage life he again made his own lab for Electronics Associate Engineering studies and in whole 3 years he got many awards and recognition for experiments in District and also in whole collage. I remember when Zaheer nominated for a Top in Punjab State with A+ and 1400 people was in front of as crowed. The Announcer announced all winners but didn’t made Zaheer’s Entry. After all awards Zaheer’s Drawing Teacher made an entry and he started to name characteristics and after 10 minutes of appraising he announced Zaheer’s Name for Award.

Again in 3rd year of Electronics Engineering he faced health issues but after some months he get completely fit. Zaheer passed Electronics Engineering Associate Degree with 78% marks.
### UNIVERSITY LIFE
Zaheer mainly wanted to go to a Electronics Engineering Institute bu later he got a selection with top in Entry Test list of Punjab University Collage of  Information Technology with 82.5% marks highest in 2011 Entry Test.

When he got admitted he again faced serious health Issue and in 2nd to 4th semester he jest tried to pass subjects with 50% but later he successfully defeated health problems he got his BS Computer Science Honors Degree with good grades.
### PROGRAMMING PROJECTS
Zaheer was involved in many of Programming Projects in University for his studies in each semester and major are following:

* C++ Wifi Chat and Encrypted file transfer tool(C++ Network Programming) Console
* C++ Snack Game with Sound, Time, Levels(With Umar Hayat) Interactive
* C++ Pop Star Game(Using GUI Libraries) Interactive
* C++ Artificial Intelligence Psychology Analyzer Connsole
* C# Boutique Management System Interactive
* Assembly TIC TAC TOE Console with colors.
 In Final year of Degree Zaheer involved in a Heavy Final Year Project in security. He choses Android app naming in “Vulnerable Apps Detector App”. Although he completed before deadline because some class fellow think Zaheer can’t be successfully done with security app so he did before enemy lines.
### CAREER
After a 4 year Honors degree of Computer Science Zaheer Moved to Islamabad Pakistan and Joined DNSPAK as Android Developer and worked for a year in. In DNSPAK Zaheer developed many android applications like Native Apps, Web Apps and also Hybrid Apps. Some of the Apps are following.

* ICMS App
* Cafe Day Dream
* Win Win Associates
* Bharakahu Property
* Sheikh Enterprises App
After in May 2016 Zaheer Resigned Due to a Financial Crises and Bankruptcy of DNSPAK.
